@startuml
Here is the corrected PlantUML for the Online College Magazine System:

title UML State Machine Diagram

state StartChoice <<choice>> [valid]
state AdminChoice <<choice>> [valid]
state EditorChoice <<choice>> [valid]
state ReadFeedbackChoice <<choice>> [valid]
state EndJoin <<choice>>

[*] --> StartChoice

state Register
Register : do / Fill details
Register : exit / Registration successful

state Login
Login : entry / Registered user
Login : do / Enter login credentials
Login : exit / Valid username and password [valid]
Login : exit / Invalid username or password [invalid]

state "Manage profiles" as ManageProfiles
ManageProfiles : entry / Admin logged in
ManageProfiles : do / Manage profile in database
ManageProfiles : do / Add, delete or edit profiles if necessary
ManageProfiles : exit / Action completed [valid]
ManageProfiles : exit / Error occurred during action [invalid]

state "Invalid user" as InvalidUser
InvalidUser : entry / Invalid login or invalid registration
InvalidUser : do / Block entry to system
InvalidUser : exit / Abnormal termination [invalid]

state Writing
Writing : entry / Writer logged in
Writing : do / Write article
Writing : exit / Send to editor [valid]
Writing : exit / Error occurred during writing [invalid]

state Editing
Editing : entry / Editor logged in and article to be edited
Editing : do / Edit article
Editing : exit / Send to moderator/admin [valid]
Editing : exit / Error occurred during editing [invalid]

state Publishing
Publishing : entry / Admin logged in and article to be approved
Publishing : do / Choose to approve and publish or reject article
Publishing : do / Add article to database if approved [valid]
Publishing : exit / Article not published [invalid]

state Search
Search : entry / Choose to search for articles
Search : do / Read searched articles
Search : exit / Completed reading [valid]
Search : exit / Error occurred during searching [invalid]

state Reading
Reading : entry / Published article
Reading : do / Read article
Reading : exit / Completed reading [valid]
Reading : exit / Error occurred during reading [invalid]

state Feedback
Feedback : entry / Reader chosen to give feedback
Feedback : do / Get feedback
Feedback : exit / Feedback entry successful [valid]
Feedback : exit / Error occurred during feedback [invalid]

StartChoice --> Register
StartChoice --> Login

Register --> AdminChoice
Login --> EditorChoice

AdminChoice --> ManageProfiles
AdminChoice --> InvalidUser

EditorChoice --> Writing
EditorChoice --> Editing
EditorChoice --> InvalidUser

Writing --> Editing
Editing --> Publishing
ManageProfiles --> Publishing

InvalidUser --> EndJoin
Publishing --> Reading
Reading --> Search
Reading --> ReadFeedbackChoice

Search --> Search
ReadFeedbackChoice --> Feedback

Feedback --> EndJoin
EndJoin --> [*]
@enduml
